<p>How does this game look so much like anime? Because it literally IS anime. All the characters are hand drawn. Only the backgrounds are 3D. I would love to see more games in this ultra hi rez, nicely hand drawn style! Imagine a fighting game with this level of craft &amp; fidelity!</p>
